                    </button>
                </div>
                <p class=" text-end text-success">今日付NT$0。房費將直接付款給住宿。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 order-0 order-lg-1">
            <div class="card mb-3">
                <div class="row g-0">
                    <div class="col-md-5 m-auto">
                        <img class="mw-100" src="./images/linus-mimietz-sgIhwj4cSiU-unsplash.jpg">
